    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-11-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-11-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="132" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d132">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 23,
                            1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Secretary of state for foreign affairs has presented impressive reasons for
                        not withdrawing seal fishery negotiations from British ambassador at
                        Washington. Satisfactory explanation by cable impracticable. Will
                        communicate immediately.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
